Summary: Create a [plan](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/plannerplan?view=graph-rest-beta) in a user [container](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/plannerplancontainer?view=graph-rest-beta) to let individual users track their own tasks. This provides the flexibility for users to share or collaborate on their personal plans, or subsequently upgrade their personal plans into group-based plans by [moving](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/plannerplan-movetocontainer?view=graph-rest-beta) the plan from the user container to a group container.
